title: Man holding a banner
description: Banner features leave messages in multiple languages. Phototgraphers' description: photos and video of Jan 29-Feb 11, 2011, Protests (downtown) & celebration in Maadi. Text in image: GO AWAY IRSE A S'en ALLER FORTGEHEN Mubarak. Translation of text in image: GO AWAY, LEAVE, Go AWAY, GO AWAY Mubarak.
